item.title: Tilted Content Slideshow
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: This slider plays with 3D perspective and performs some interesting animations on the right-hand side images.

item.title: Tilted Items
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: The perspective view is achieved by adding a perspective value to the slide list item and tilting a division that contains the two screenshots.

item.title: CSS Animations
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: We are using 12 different animations for showing and hiding the items of a slide. The animations are defined by randomly adding data-attributes called data-effect-in and data-effect-out for every slide.
